{"tid":2157203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法新社：洛馬敲定620億美元F-16V訂單 買家包括台灣","createTime":"2020-08-15T01:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T02:25:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"991da2680a31cb35f825aff960b8ca265c62850c","tid":2157203,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:22:51.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓14日綜合外電報導）消息人士向法新社證實，美國武器製造商洛克希德馬丁（Lockheed Martin）獲得10年總價共620億美元的F-16V訂單，其中要提供給台灣的部分已經定案。報導並說，對台灣提供F-16V戰機一事肯定將激怒北京當局。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部宣布這項合約時沒有透露買方，但一名熟悉內情的消息人士向法新社證實是台灣。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：張曉雯/核稿：陳昱婷）1090815<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008150013.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202008150013.aspx&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=a257037d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008150013.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"f5afeb0e21c3da99aed7643a3c125d32b4721c04","tid":2157203,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國防部14日公布軍售合約，包含美國武器製造商洛克希德馬丁（Lockheed Martin）的90架F-16戰機，儘管並未指明買方，但美國媒體透露，這其中包含台灣購買的66架新式F-16戰機，消息可能會令美國與中國關係進一步緊張。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》 報導，這是自1992年時任美國總統老布希（George H. W. Bush）批准向台灣出售150架F-16戰機以來，華府再次向台灣出售同類戰機。本次合約總值620億美元，超過美國10年來，准許外國潛在買家容許購買的上限。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，美國國防部公布的軍售合約，顯示洛克希德馬丁打造的90架F-16戰機<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息人士還透露，出售到台灣的F-16戰鬥機將配備&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;，其中新購66架F-16系列戰機，預估2023年可取得美方首批交貨的兩架新機，2026年可將66架新機交機工作全數完成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3260923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3260923&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8Rzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=405e4c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3260923&h=e5550afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3260923</a><br />\n<br />\n66架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c19c1ec880b2893fe688141d5919f0b7638d544","tid":2157203,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"200架啦"},{"pid":"c1d4b347e74646aa8b786ba9a2dccfeb1e539570","tid":2157203,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"china joe 上台就唔會賣比台灣"},{"pid":"537d478e702118b3130f25dca157762eb95d6683","tid":2157203,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d4b347e74646aa8b786ba9a2dccfeb1e539570","tid":2157203,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"china joe 上台就唔會賣比台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:25:18.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到咁得唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}